IMQD_HUSR_ID <> DEBC_EMP_HANDLING (DEBC_NO = IMQD_DEBC_NO)
If IMQD_IMQH_TYPE = 7 (legal collection) and GNRL_CODE = PL then set IMQD_HUSR_ID = CLNT205_EMP_CONTACT
(AK SCR13317)
Rarely it happens that two jobs at the very same time tries to add the same row
in the table in this case we get a duplicate index and the program is
turning to MSGW.
When it happens we want to avoid MSGW and jus t cancel the update action.
